0 of byte 0 in the file B3, and `F8:1` points to the float 1 at the file F8.\n\n\n### About routing\n\nThe configuration of routing follows a very special syntax for now\n\n    0x01,0x00,0x01,0x00\n      |    |    |    |\n      |    |    |    +-- 0: The slot of the PLC\n      |    |    +------- 1: Route over the backplane\n      |    +------------ Reserved, always zero\n      +----------------- 1: Number of words (1 = 2 bytes) of the routing section\n\nYou most likely just want to change the last number to the slot of the PLC when connecting to ControlLogix/CompactLogix controllers\n\n\n## Wishlist\n- Validate addresses\n- Improve routing configuration\n\n\n## Bugs and enhancements\n\nPlease share your ideas and experiences on the [Node-RED forum](https://discourse.nodered.org/), or open an issue on the [page of the project on GitHub](https://github.com/st-one-io/node-red-contrib-pccc)\n\n\n## License\nCopyright: (c) 2016-2021, [ST-One Ltda.](https://st-one.io)\n\nGNU General Public License v3.0+ (see [LICENSE](LICENSE) or https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt)\n","maintainers":[{"email":"fernandogabriel1703@gmail.com","name":"fernandoamorim"},{"email":"daniel.michalichyn@outlook.com","name":"daniel.michalichyn"},{"email":"gfcittolin@gmail.com","name":"gfcittolin"},{"email":"machado.ti@gmail.com","name":"machadotiago"}],"time":{"modified":"2023-06-21T17:39:29.269Z","created":"2017-08-28T18:58:34.529Z","0.1.1":"2017-08-28T18:58:34.529Z","1.0.0-0":"2019-10-31T19:32:26.508Z","1.0.0":"2019-10-31T20:18:41.847Z","1.0.1":"2020-05-24T23:52:47.557Z","1.0.2":"2021-06-22T00:35:58.368Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/st-one-io/node-red-contrib-pccc#readme","keywords":["hardware","allen-bradley","rockwell","plc","micrologix","controllogix","compactlogix","ethernet-ip","node-red"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/st-one-io/node-red-contrib-pccc.git"},"author":{"name":"ST-One Ltda."},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/st-one-io/node-red-contrib-pccc/issu